What's your relationship with Shuo Xuan?

187
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:08,400
What are you talking about?

188
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:12,100
I have no idea what you mean.

189
00:18:12,100 --> 00:18:14,400
Who is Shuo Xuan?

190
00:18:29,719 --> 00:18:33,159
You demon. Are you still not going to tell us?

191
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:36,560
It seems I can't hide it anymore.

192
00:18:40,959 --> 00:18:45,320
Young Lord, please forgive my earlier rudeness.

193
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:48,100
Me?

194
00:18:49,100 --> 00:18:52,600
Young Qi is actually the young lord of our Yu Clan.

195
00:18:52,600 --> 00:18:53,800
Fish? 
  (Homophones) 

196
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:56,300
- What? 
 - The Y-Yu Clan?

197
00:18:56,300 --> 00:18:59,400
The Yu Clan are sea demons living in the Sea and Clear Skies.

198
00:18:59,400 --> 00:19:02,600
Miss Yue is a demon?

199
00:19:02,600 --> 00:19:05,900
But Young Yue has no demonic aura.

200
00:19:06,700 --> 00:19:08,200
Her Lordship of the Yu Clan, Zhu Yu,

201
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:11,400
is a mythical beast that has existed since ancient times.

202
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:14,000
You can't compare her to any other demon.

203
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:18,600
You say Qi is your Lord's child.

204
00:19:18,600 --> 00:19:21,800
Then, why did you abandon her in the Mortal Realm,

205
00:19:21,800 --> 00:19:24,900
completely ignoring her for three years?

206
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:31,000
This is Her Lordship's punishment for you, so you ended up becoming a mortal

207
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:33,800
stranded in the Mortal Realm.

208
00:19:33,800 --> 00:19:35,600
Punishment?

209
00:19:35,600 --> 00:19:39,450
D-Did Young Yue do something wrong?

210
00:19:40,200 --> 00:19:44,600
We have a forbidden technique called the Companion Life Spell.

211
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:47,000
If it's cast on someone,

212
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:50,400
that person will lose their memory

213
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:53,600
and their previous personality will be erased.

214
00:19:53,600 --> 00:19:57,500
From then on, this person must live for the one who used the technique

215
00:19:57,500 --> 00:20:02,200
and protect that person their whole life.

216
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:07,800
Losing their personality and memory,

217
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:11,800
and living only for another person from then on.

218
00:20:11,800 --> 00:20:15,500
Yes. Three years ago, our young lord traveled in the Mortal Realm.

219
00:20:15,500 --> 00:20:21,400
When passing by Wuyan Village, she unintentionally used the Companion Life Spell on a young mortal.

220
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:24,800
Once this spell is cast, it can't be undone.

221
00:20:24,800 --> 00:20:27,000
Her Lordship loves you,

222
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:30,200
but it was such a grave mistake, so you couldn't go unpunished.

223
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:33,700
Thus, Her Lordship erased your memory, turning you into a whole new person

224
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:36,600
to better reflect on yourself in the Mortal Realm.

225
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:42,500
Could that mortal youth be Brother Yue?

226
00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:43,600
Over these three years,

227
00:20:43,600 --> 00:20:46,300
