251
00:23:34,900 --> 00:23:37,400
For years, you have been persistent in eradicating demons.

252
00:23:37,400 --> 00:23:41,300
That's because I was young then. I couldn't protect her.

253
00:23:41,300 --> 00:23:45,500
But now, I absolutely will not allow demons to do wrong in front of me.

254
00:23:45,500 --> 00:23:49,200
But, Young Xiu, you want to eradicate demons,

255
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:52,400
